prompts.frontCover:
A vibrant and funny watercolor illustration for a birthday card front, set on a sunny, sandy beach with a bright blue sky and gentle ocean waves in the background. In the center, a cartoon depiction of an elderly Asian woman, Lao Lao, sits majestically on an ornate throne constructed entirely of mahjong tiles (green dragons, red dragons, winds, bamboos, etc.). She wears a playful crown, a big happy smile, and is holding a comically oversized bubble tea with large boba pearls. To her left, stands a cartoon version of the young man (Jordan) from the reference photo, with short black hair, a broad white-toothed smile, and a white t-shirt, cheering her on. The scene is painted in a soft, flowing watercolor style with visible brush strokes, organic paint bleeds, and a subtle paper texture. In the center of the illustration, written in a beautiful, readable, handwritten cursive script, is the text "Happy Birthday".

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
